Class Description
CheesesteakFundraiser
Manages data and operations related to a cheesesteak fundraiser event, including loading member sales data, calculating shared values, and generating aggregate and individual sales reports.
MemberSale
Represents a member's sales information including small, large, and combo sales, as well as total sales, club fundraising total, and tax allocation.
Project3
Description of Project3 Manages the main functionality and user interface for Project3, a cheesesteak fundraiser data manipulation program.
